Text: RE FW Oh SusanPlease respond to You would love all and not just one of the Eaters I will be up here until I get a new job So that is hard to tell Ill catch you later and hope that some rest lies in your future MR Original Message From mailto Sent Monday April PM To Subject Re FW Oh Susan Thanks for thinking of me the ride back was lovely lots of gummy food items and carbonated beveragesim very tired from all of the weekend activity though and dont see much rest in my future Oh well life is short right Im so glad we were able to spend some time together this weekend and that you got a chance to meet my parents Im going to have to make a trip up to Austin soon for a visit to make sure youre hitting all the must seeseats By the way how long are you going to be there Susan Maybe Ill hit an Eaters outing Embedded Enron Capital Trade Resources Corp image moved to file From Mary Rebecca Harp picpcx PM Please respond to To cc Subject FW Oh Susan Well that clarified it How are you doing I hope that you and Jen had a safe trip back to Houston I thought of you this morning when the Uncle Kracker song popped up on sonicnet Song is Follow Me and the album is Double Wide Classy classy Have a great week and hope to catch up soon MR Original Message From Scott Susan mailto Sent Monday April PM To Subject RE Oh Susan Since I dont recognize your name try there are Susan Scotts at Enron Original Message From Mary Rebecca Harp ENRON mailtoIMCEANOTESMaryRebeccaHarpCmharpaustinEa pcEslbEcomE NRONcom Sent Monday April PM To Scott Susan Subject Oh Susan is this you MR
